{"id": 2908, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都发现了哪些堪称“线上交情探测仪”的操作？", "description": "嗯，互联网的确可能让“友谊”变得更像试错游戏了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock ）", "record_count": 1248, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201904221711446Oc9RpwG5aLjtBJn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 341310, "content": "若不是兴趣相投，都是笑话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497407}, {"id": 341314, "content": "朋友圈广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282958}, {"id": 341316, "content": "打个电话聊不了几句", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605725}, {"id": 341318, "content": "热点屏蔽我不会(ΘˍΘ=)我对各种迥异的观点都抱有好奇心，无论多脑残(ﾉ_ _)ﾉ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633898}, {"id": 340554, "content": "每当社会热点大事发生时刷一刷朋友圈，是时候屏蔽／清理一波好友了", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 340555, "content": "发一些灵魂测试/熟悉度测试", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 340556, "content": "难过时候发歌词／换相册封面，隐蔽地发现谁是在关心你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 341325, "content": "群发什么“我们是什么关系 转x钱”的网络乞丐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645165}, {"id": 341327, "content": "发消息给他或她，不回，朋友圈却在之后发了条，可以删好友了，真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645174}, {"id": 341342, "content": "秒回那条不赞成。及时回复别人消息是我个人的原则，但是经常会不看手机，所以秒回只是因为刚好看到了消息哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518777}, {"id": 341343, "content": "帮点外卖红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551188}, {"id": 341345, "content": "有耐心抚慰我的负面情绪，并且在事后多次关心我啊情绪状况", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629594}, {"id": 343914, "content": "借钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644468}, {"id": 346221, "content": "双方互相关心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 341359, "content": "聊着聊着，一方突然断片儿，然后过了段时间，双方就刚刚的话题接着聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145894}, {"id": 342665, "content": "斗图", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329164}, {"id": 341386, "content": "在吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640200}, {"id": 341390, "content": "不回复微信的两分钟后却发了一条朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447825}, {"id": 341391, "content": "可以因为手头有重要事而不秒回并且大胆承认老子没秒回你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471603}, {"id": 341168, "content": "积赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535118}, {"id": 341169, "content": "点赞之交，比点头之交，更不可交。", "image": null, "praise_count": 224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294190}, {"id": 341170, "content": "在对方不喜欢的话题边缘试探，试探对方底线。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957543}, {"id": 341171, "content": "对方愿意为了你放弃自己的某些利益，那绝对是好朋友了", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644423}, {"id": 341173, "content": "随时能约出来，随时可以打扰或者被打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 179, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 341174, "content": "借钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128485}, {"id": 341175, "content": "借钱，数目不多，然后就消失了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841095}, {"id": 341176, "content": "只是谁都给点赞，只是谁都不给点赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 341177, "content": "平时不联系，婚礼发邀请，还是微信链接那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633518}, {"id": 341182, "content": "屏蔽我的朋友圈，他的朋友圈对我不可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590940}, {"id": 341185, "content": "现实中交情好的朋友可能网络上聊天一个表情包都不会用，网络上认识的朋友，疯狂用表情包缓解尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615130}, {"id": 341204, "content": "回复评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 341205, "content": "表情包那个不太同意耶。熟人之间表情包用的更多，很喜欢各种有趣的表情包。不熟的人反而会收敛严肃一些~", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488020}, {"id": 341206, "content": "他朋友圈发了最新的动态或者日常，会不会去下面留言聊上一两句", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428396}, {"id": 341208, "content": "秒回。", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 341209, "content": "别设置备注 如果1500个好友你还能记得3/4的人都是谁 说明这都是你的活跃好友 而不是名片互换换来的点头之交", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644909}, {"id": 341210, "content": "分享的链接，愿意看，并能转发的，是真正志同道合的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637829}, {"id": 341213, "content": "性向", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461099}, {"id": 341216, "content": "个人感觉秒回的一定是很重要的列表好友吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117319}, {"id": 341219, "content": "群发智障清好友信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644123}, {"id": 341225, "content": "我关闭了朋友圈，怎么说", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437639}, {"id": 341243, "content": "我主要还是看现实中的交往。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}]}